snippet.title: Song of the Deep - Official Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Dive even further into Merryn's Adventure with the official Song of the Deep Launch Trailer! Showcasing a brilliant underwater world and fast-paced combat leading up to launch, get a final look into the game from the perspective of Merryn's father.

http://www.songofthedeep.com
